    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency in Test conditions (achieved 2, required 3) is acknowledged and accepted given the scope of the F1717 protocol. Overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission claim for this assessment.",
